    AU - type of AppUser
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, TableStructureContributer<AU>, HistoryFieldContributor, ParseFactory<AU>, SummaryContributer<AU>, MenuContributor<AU>

    public class EmailNameFinder<AU extends AppUser>
extends AppUserNameFinder<AU,EmailNameFinder<AU>>
implements HistoryFieldContributor, SummaryContributer<AU>, MenuContributor<AU>
    A AppUserNameFinder to handle users canonical Email The email address is required not to resolve to an existing name on the factory unless it corresponds to the current object. (we query the full factory in case we have a NameFinder for known aliases as well.

    spb
